Changelog:
4.1.3: Zombies aggro once player is within 500 blocks range.
    Zombies pillar and bridge their way to player if allowed. 
4.1.2:  Blazes will no longer use flame touch effect on push attacker away unless Flame Touch is set to true in config.
		Entities should no longer crash server when trying to find and ride a spider mount
		Removed cave spider from default riders for spider rider
		Zombies can break blocks now
4.1.1:  Fixed crash/bug with Zombie Pigman feature when player breaks blocks (see issue #32)
		Zombie Pigman features and AI should all work now
4.1.0: 	Initial alpha release
